### Health check
GET http://localhost:5007/health

### User list - should still work after Router refactor
GET http://localhost:5007/users

### Create user - should still work after Router refactor
POST http://localhost:5007/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mali",
  "email": "mali@example.com"
}

### Invalid user create - should return 400
POST http://localhost:5007/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mali"
}

### Product list - private fields must disappear after DTO task
GET http://localhost:5007/products

### Create product - private input fields must be ignored after DTO task
POST http://localhost:5007/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop Stand",
  "category": "Accessories",
  "price": 790,
  "cost_price": 310,
  "supplier_note": "Client must not control this field"
}
